txt.en: 'Well done [placeholder]. It might not seem much, but every bit will aid the war effort. We still need to gather much before we will be ready to march forward.\n\n'Hopefully this sends a message to those thieves, and we can take inventory of what is available without worrying about anything else going missing.'
The stolen army supplies can be found in the abandoned district to the north-east of Tol Ciryarani.\n\nYou should reclaim the stolen supplies.
Thandor, the Gondorian Captain, can be located in the market east of Tol Ciryarani.\n\nYou should speak with Thandor.
Many supplies went missing during the Battle at Pelargir, and Thandor has asked you to locate where they went.

'After the battle, we noticed that some of our supply caches began to mysteriously dwindle. We traced this back to a group of ruffians who have taken up shelter in an abandoned part of the east-garth. I cannot tell you how many brave souls gave everything to protect this city, and this criminal element seeks to profit from it!\n\n'We would ask you to bring back any supplies you might find from that place.'
